---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Gear | Teddy Travels">
  <h1>Gear</h1>
  <p>
    Notes on the stuff I use outside: what worked, what failed, what was worth
    the money, and what I would change next time.
  </p>

  <div class="card-grid gear-grid">
    <a class="card" href="/gear/backpacking">
      <h2>Backpacking</h2>
      <p>Packs, tents, sleeping bags, pads, stoves, water filters, layers, and camp systems.</p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/gear/running">
      <h2>Running</h2>
      <p>Shoes, watches, shorts, hydration, race gear, and training stuff that actually matters.</p>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="/gear/climbing-snow">
      <h2>Climbing & Snow</h2>
      <p>Boots, axes, crampons, helmets, ski gear, glacier gear, and future alpine systems.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
